name: iPhone Templates
description:
Quick-start iOS projects with templates for iPhone 13, 13 Mini, 13 Pro, 13 Pro Max, 12, 12 Mini, 12 Pro, 12 Pro Max, and SE 2nd gen.


INCLUDES:


📐Rulers for placement of common iOS elements

  • 🍔 Page actions
  • 🔠 Page title
  • 🔍 Search bar
  • ✈️ Tab bar
  • 🏠 Home bar

⏱Single-layer status bar for easy modification

📱Single-layer outline and notch for realistic device preview

🔗 Link to visual overview of iOS design guidelines for easy reference
